// pipe_a.ember — stage A of the dataflow pipeline test (Family C: ember pipe).
// A single-arg i64->i64 function `process` that adds 1 to its input. This is
// the first stage of the linear chain A.process -> B.reduce (-> C.square).
//
// Loaded by `ember pipe tests/features/pipe_2stage.pipe` (and the 3-stage /
// .em-bundler configs). The pipe runner compiles this module, looks up
// `process` by name, and calls it per stream value.
fn process(x: i64) -> i64 {
    return x + 1;
}
